{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775894967790,"sessionID":"ses_2846be6dbffem0trR4hEIofkpE","part":{"id":"prt_d7b96b1a5001596nHjqktem6TQ","messageID":"msg_d7b96a8d9001EOoI775NaAPsLv","sessionID":"ses_2846be6dbffem0trR4hEIofkpE","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_48292b29698143cf963f70e7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/workloadmanager\n4: **Language:** Go\n5: **Size:** L\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块补齐缺失的 Go 单元测试，覆盖 reconciler 核心协调逻辑、handler sandbox 创建流程、及顶层常量定义。已有测试（response、lifecycle、delete、metrics）保持不变。目标是提升关键路径代码覆盖率、防止回归、为后续重构提供安全网。\n10: \n11: ## Scope\n12: \n13: ### In Scope\n14: \n15: 1. **reconciler/reconciler_test.go** — `SandboxReconciler` 生命周期测试\n16:    - `NewSandboxReconciler` 参数校验（nil Store/Clientset/InformerFactory panic）\n17:    - `Run` 幂等性（重复调用忽略）、cache sync 成功/失败路径\n18:    - `Enqueue` key 格式（带/不带 namespace）、metrics 触发\n19:    - `WatchSandboxOnce` 正常返回、超时返回\n20: \n21: 2. **reconciler/sync_test.go** — 工作队列与 sync 流程测试\n22:    - `syncHandler` key 解析（有效/无效格式）\n23:    - AgentRuntime 存在 → `reconcileAgentRuntime`\n24:    - CodeInterpreter 存在 → `reconcileCodeInterpreter`\n25:    - Pod 存在 → `reconcilePod`\n26:    - 三者均不存在 → 返回 nil\n27:    - `processNextWorkItem` 重试逻辑（maxRetries=15、指数退避、超时强制退出）\n28:    - `determineResourceType` 根据 lister 结果推断资源类型\n29: \n30: 3. **reconciler/agentruntime_test.go** — AgentRuntime 协调测试\n31:    - `mapConditionToStatus` 条件映射（Ready=True→running、Ready=False+Terminated→terminated、Ready=False→pending、Ready=Unknown→pending、无条件→pending）\n32:    - `reconcileAgentRuntime` 正常路径：lister 获取 → session-id 标签 → Store 不存在则 StoreSandbox、存在且状态变化则 UpdateSandbox\n33:    - DeletionTimestamp 非空 → DeleteSandboxBySessionID\n34:    - session-id 标签缺失 → 跳过\n35:    - Store 操作失败 → 返回错误 + metrics 记录\n36: \n37: 4. **reconciler/codeinterpreter_test.go** — CodeInterpreter 协调测试\n38:    - 与 AgentRuntime 对称的测试场景\n39:    - WarmPoolSize > 0 日志路径验证\n40:    - Kind 字段为 \"CodeInterpreter\"\n41: \n42: 5. **reconciler/pod_test.go** — Pod 协调测试\n43:    - `reconcilePod` 正常路径：sandbox-name 标签 → Pod Running + IP 非空 → ListSandboxes 匹配 → UpdateSandbox PodIP\n44:    - sandbox-name 标签缺失 → 跳过\n45:    - Pod 非 Running 或 IP 为空 → 跳过\n46:    - PodIP 未变化 → 跳过\n47:    - `buildEntryPointsFromSandboxInfo` 端点 IP 替换\n48:    - `extractPort` 端口提取（含/不含冒号）\n49: \n50: 6. **reconciler/event_handlers_test.go** — 事件处理器测试\n51:    - AgentRuntime Add/Update/Delete → workqueue.Add + metrics\n52:    - CodeInterpreter Add/Update/Delete → workqueue.Add + metrics\n53:    - Pod Add → sandbox-name 标签检查 → workqueue.Add\n54:    - Pod Update → oldRunning→newRunning 或 ipChanged 才入队\n55:    - Pod Delete → 仅日志，不入队\n56:    - `cache.DeletedFinalStateUnknown` tombstone 处理\n57: \n58: 7. **handler/sandbox_create_test.go** — Sandbox 创建 handler 测试\n59:    - `CreateSandboxRequest.Validate` 校验（kind/namespace/name 必填、kind 枚举值）\n60:    - `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 请求解析 → template 查找 → sessionID/sandboxName 生成 → CR 构建 → StoreSandbox → WatchSandboxOnce → dynamicClient.Create → PodIP 解析 → UpdateSandbox → 响应\n61:    - `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` 同上 + WarmPoolSize > 0 → SandboxClaim 路径\n62:    - `injectPicodAuthEnv` AuthModePicoD 注入\n63:    - `rollbackCR` 回滚逻辑（正常删除、AlreadyNotFound）\n64:    - `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR` CR 构建（labels、annotations、spec、podTemplate 转换）\n65:    - `buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR` CR 构建（warm pool 分支、Sandbox vs SandboxClaim）\n66:    - `resolvePodIP` 多种解析策略（直接 Get、Annotation、LabelSelector + OwnerReference）\n67:    - `buildEntryPoints` 端点构建\n68:    - `generateSessionID` / `generateSandboxName` / `RandString`\n69:    - `getDynamicClient` auth 开启/关闭、token cache、user client factory\n70: \n71: 8. **const.go** — 顶层常量验证\n72:    - `LastActivityAnnotationKey` 值验证\n73: \n74: ### Out of Scope\n75: \n76: - 集成测试（需要真实 Kubernetes API server）\n77: - E2E 测试（需要完整 AgentCube 平台环境）\n78: - 性能/基准测试（后续单独 AR）\n79: - 修改 workloadmanager 生产代码（仅新增 `*_test.go` 文件）\n80: - 已有测试文件的修改（response_test.go、sandbox_lifecycle_test.go、sandbox_delete_test.go、metrics_test.go）\n81: \n82: ## Architecture Summary\n83: \n84: ### Current State\n85: \n86: `pkg/workloadmanager/` 模块结构：\n87: \n88: ```\n89: pkg/workloadmanager/\n90: ├── const.go                          # 顶层常量\n91: ├── handler/\n92: │   ├── constants.go                  # GVR、Kind、Label、Annotation 常量\n93: │   ├── models.go                     # 数据模型 + MetricsRecorder 接口\n94: │   ├── sandbox_create.go             # Sandbox 创建 handler（AgentRuntime + CodeInterpreter）\n95: │   ├── sandbox_delete.go             # Sandbox 删除 handler\n96: │   ├── sandbox_lifecycle.go          # 生命周期管理（GC、TTL、idle、status、list、extend）\n97: │   ├── sandbox_lifecycle_test.go     # ✅ 已有测试\n98: │   └── sandbox_delete_test.go        # ✅ 已有测试\n99: ├── reconciler/\n100: │   ├── reconciler.go                 # SandboxReconciler 主控制器\n101: │   ├── sync.go                       # syncHandler + workqueue 处理\n102: │   ├── agentruntime.go               # AgentRuntime 协调逻辑\n103: │   ├── codeinterpreter.go            # CodeInterpreter 协调逻辑\n104: │   ├── pod.go                        # Pod 协调逻辑\n105: │   ├── event_handlers.go             # Informer 事件处理\n106: │   ├── types.go                      # Store 接口 + ReconcilerDeps\n107: │   ├── metrics.go                    # PrometheusMetricsRecorder\n108: │   └── metrics_test.go               # ✅ 已有测试\n109: └── response/\n110:     ├── response.go                   # HTTP 响应工具\n111:     └── response_test.go              # ✅ 已有测试\n112: ```\n113: \n114: **已有测试覆盖**：\n115: - `response/` — JSON/Error/Created/ErrorWithID 全部覆盖\n116: - `handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go` — LifecycleManager 构造、过期判断、Start/Stop、GetSandboxStatus、ListSandboxes、ExtendSandboxTTL、GC 清理、边界条件\n117: - `handler/sandbox_delete_test.go` — DeleteSandboxRequest 校验、resolveGVR、MockStore 全操作\n118: - `reconciler/metrics_test.go` — PrometheusMetricsRecorder 全部方法 + nil receiver 安全\n119: \n120: **测试缺口**：\n121: - `reconciler/` — 核心协调逻辑（reconciler.go、sync.go、agentruntime.go、codeinterpreter.go、pod.go、event_handlers.go）完全无测试\n122: - `handler/sandbox_create.go` — 创建流程完全无测试\n123: - `const.go` — 顶层常量无验证\n124: \n125: ### Target State\n126: \n127: 新增以下测试文件，与现有测试风格一致（testify + table-driven + mock）：\n128: \n129: | 文件 | 覆盖目标 |\n130: |------|----------|\n131: | `reconciler/reconciler_test.go` | NewSandboxReconciler、Run、Enqueue、WatchSandboxOnce |\n132: | `reconciler/sync_test.go` | syncHandler、processNextWorkItem、determineResourceType |\n133: | `reconciler/agentruntime_test.go` | mapConditionToStatus、reconcileAgentRuntime |\n134: | `reconciler/codeinterpreter_test.go` | reconcileCodeInterpreter |\n135: | `reconciler/pod_test.go` | reconcilePod、buildEntryPointsFromSandboxInfo、extractPort |\n136: | `reconciler/event_handlers_test.go` | 9 个事件处理函数 |\n137: | `handler/sandbox_create_test.go` | 创建流程全路径 |\n138: | `const_test.go` | 顶层常量验证 |\n139: \n140: ## Impact Analysis\n141: \n142: ### Dependencies\n143: \n144: | 依赖 | 来源 | 说明 |\n145: |------|------|------|\n146: | `testing` | Go stdlib | 标准测试框架 |\n147: | `github.com/stretchr/testify` | go.mod | 断言库（项目已使用） |\n148: | `net/http/httptest` | Go stdlib | HTTP handler 测试 |\n149: | `k8s.io/client-go/dynamic/fake` | go.mod | fake dynamic client |\n150: | `k8s.io/client-go/testing` | go.mod | reactor 机制 |\n151: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime` | go.mod | scheme 注册 |\n152: \n153: ### Affected Components\n154: \n155: | 文件/目录 | 状态 | 说明 |\n156: |-----------|------|------|\n157: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler_test.go` | 新增 | Reconciler 生命周期测试 |\n158: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sync_test.go` | 新增 | Sync 流程测试 |\n159: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime_test.go` | 新增 | AgentRuntime 协调测试 |\n160: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/codeinterpreter_test.go` | 新增 | CodeInterpreter 协调测试 |\n161: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/pod_test.go` | 新增 | Pod 协调测试 |\n162: | `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/event_handlers_test.go` | 新增 | 事件处理测试 |\n163: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_create_test.go` | 新增 | 创建 handler 测试 |\n164: | `pkg/workloadmanager/const_test.go` | 新增 | 顶层常量验证 |\n165: | `pkg/workloadmanager/` | 无变更 | 生产代码不修改 |\n166: \n167: ### Risk Assessment\n168: \n169: | 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n170: |------|------|----------|\n171: | `SandboxReconciler.Run` 阻塞式调用难以在单测中验证 | 高 | 使用 goroutine + channel 传递结果，设置超时 |\n172: | Informer factory 需要真实 client 或复杂 mock | 高 | 使用 `fake.NewSimpleDynamicClient` + 手动触发 informer 事件 |\n173: | `WatchSandboxOnce` 依赖 lister 异步填充 | 中 | 使用 channel 控制 lister 返回时机 |\n174: | `processNextWorkItem` 重试逻辑涉及时间（指数退避） | 中 | mock workqueue 或使用 `FakeRateLimitingQueue` |\n175: | sandbox_create 涉及 dynamic client + kube clientset 双重依赖 | 中 | 分别 mock，使用 fake clientset + fake dynamic client |\n176: | 测试数据构造复杂（CR 结构、pod spec 转换） | 低 | 复用现有 `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR` 逻辑验证输出结构 |\n177: \n178: ## Alternatives Considered\n179: \n180: ### 1. Table-driven tests vs. individual test functions（✅ 选定 table-driven）\n181: \n182: - **Table-driven**：Go 惯用法，易于扩展，减少样板代码，与现有测试风格一致\n183: - **Individual functions**：每个场景独立函数，更清晰但冗余\n184: - **决策**：以 table-driven 为主（`mapConditionToStatus`、`extractPort`、事件处理等），复杂异步场景辅以独立函数（`Run`、`WatchSandboxOnce`）\n185: \n186: ### 2. testify vs. 标准库（✅ 选定 testify）\n187: \n188: - **testify**：项目已使用 `github.com/stretchr/testify/assert` 和 `require`，保持一致\n189: - **标准库**：零依赖，但断言需手动实现\n190: - **决策**：跟随项目现有测试风格\n191: \n192: ### 3. Mock interface vs. fake clientset（✅ 选定混合策略）\n193: \n194: - **Mock interface**：对 `Store`、`MetricsRecorder` 使用手写 mock（已有 `mockStore` 模式）\n195: - **Fake clientset**：对 Kubernetes 客户端使用 `k8s.io/client-go` 内置 fake 实现\n196: - **决策**：Store/MetricsRecorder 用手写 mock（简单可控），Kubernetes 客户端用 fake（行为真实）\n197: \n198: ### 4. 测试完整 Run 循环 vs. 拆分测试（✅ 选定拆分测试）\n199: \n200: - **完整 Run 循环**：启动真实 informer + workqueue + workers，验证端到端\n201: - **拆分测试**：分别测试 NewSandboxReconciler、Enqueue、syncHandler、processNextWorkItem\n202: - **决策**：拆分测试。Run 循环涉及 goroutine 和阻塞调用，单测中难以可靠验证。通过测试各组件间接保证 Run 正确性。`WatchSandboxOnce` 作为唯一的异步公开方法单独测试。\n203: \n204: ## Upstream Dependencies\n205: \n206: - `pkg/workloadmanager/` 生产代码稳定\n207: - `client-go/` 生成的 Kubernetes 客户端代码可用（fake clientset、informers、listers）\n208: - Go 测试工具链可用（`go test`）\n209: \n210: ## Test Strategy\n211: \n212: ### Mock Objects\n213: \n214: | Mock | 用途 | 实现方式 |\n215: |------|------|----------|\n216: | `mockStore` | Store 接口模拟 | 已有（sandbox_delete_test.go 中的 `mockStore`，提取为共享 fixture） |\n217: | `mockMetricsRecorder` | MetricsRecorder 接口模拟 | 新建，记录调用次数和参数 |\n218: | `fake dynamic.Client` | Kubernetes 动态客户端 | `k8s.io/client-go/dynamic/fake` |\n219: | `fake clientset.Clientset` | 类型化客户端 | `client-go/clientset/versioned/fake` |\n220: | `fake informer factory` | Informer 工厂 | 手动构造 + 手动 Add 对象 |\n221: \n222: ### Test Categories\n223: \n224: 1. **Unit tests**（纯函数）：`mapConditionToStatus`、`extractPort`、`Validate`、`RandString`\n225: 2. **Mock-based tests**（依赖注入）：`reconcileAgentRuntime`、`reconcileCodeInterpreter`、`reconcilePod`、事件处理\n226: 3. **HTTP handler tests**（httptest）：`CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox`、`CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox`\n227: 4. **Async tests**（goroutine + channel）：`WatchSandboxOnce`\n228: \n229: ## Acceptance Criteria\n230: \n231: 1. **reconciler/**\n232:    - [ ] `NewSandboxReconciler` nil 参数 panic 测试（Store、Clientset、InformerFactory）\n233:    - [ ] `NewSandboxReconciler` 默认 workers=2 验证\n234:    - [ ] `Enqueue` 带/不带 namespace 的 key 格式验证\n235:    - [ ] `Enqueue` metricsRecorder 非空时触发 IncWorkqueueAdds\n236:    - [ ] `Run` 幂等性（重复调用返回）\n237:    - [ ] `WatchSandboxOnce` AgentRuntime 存在且 Ready → 返回 running\n238:    - [ ] `WatchSandboxOnce` 超时 → 返回 error\n239:    - [ ] `syncHandler` 无效 key → 返回错误\n240:    - [ ] `syncHandler` AgentRuntime 存在 → reconcileAgentRuntime\n241:    - [ ] `syncHandler` CodeInterpreter 存在 → reconcileCodeInterpreter\n242:    - [ ] `syncHandler` Pod 存在 → reconcilePod\n243:    - [ ] `syncHandler` 三者均不存在 → nil\n244:    - [ ] `processNextWorkItem` 错误重试（< maxRetries 入队、>= maxRetries Forget）\n245:    - [ ] `mapConditionToStatus` 全部条件分支覆盖（5 个 case）\n246:    - [ ] `reconcileAgentRuntime` 新资源 → StoreSandbox\n247:    - [ ] `reconcileAgentRuntime` 状态变化 → UpdateSandbox\n248:    - [ ] `reconcileAgentRuntime` terminated → DeleteSandboxBySessionID\n249:    - [ ] `reconcileAgentRuntime` DeletionTimestamp → DeleteSandboxBySessionID\n250:    - [ ] `reconcileAgentRuntime` session-id 缺失 → 跳过\n251:    - [ ] `reconcileCodeInterpreter` 与 AgentRuntime 对称场景\n252:    - [ ] `reconcileCodeInterpreter` WarmPoolSize > 0 日志路径\n253:    - [ ] `reconcilePod` Running + IP 变化 → UpdateSandbox\n254:    - [ ] `reconcilePod` 非 Running / 无 IP / 无 sandbox-name → 跳过\n255:    - [ ] `buildEntryPointsFromSandboxInfo` 端点 IP 替换\n256:    - [ ] `extractPort` 端口提取（含冒号、不含冒号）\n257:    - [ ] 全部 9 个事件处理函数入队验证\n258:    - [ ] Pod Update 条件过滤（oldRunning→newRunning 或 ipChanged）\n259:    - [ ] Pod Delete 仅日志不入队\n260:    - [ ] tombstone（DeletedFinalStateUnknown）处理\n261: \n262: 2. **handler/sandbox_create_test.go**\n263:    - [ ] `CreateSandboxRequest.Validate` 全部校验分支\n264:    - [ ] `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 成功路径\n265:    - [ ] `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 请求体无效 → 400\n266:    - [ ] `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` template 不存在 → 404\n267:    - [ ] `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` podTemplate 缺失 → 400\n268:    - [ ] `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` Watch 超时 → 回滚 + 500\n269:    - [ ] `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` 成功路径\n270:    - [ ] `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` WarmPoolSize > 0 → SandboxClaim\n271:    - [ ] `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox` AuthModePicoD → injectPicodAuthEnv\n272:    - [ ] `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR` 输出结构验证（labels、annotations、spec）\n273:    - [ ] `buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR` warm pool 分支 → SandboxClaim\n274:    - [ ] `buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR` 非 warm pool → Sandbox\n275:    - [ ] `resolvePodIP` 直接 Get 成功\n276:    - [ ] `resolvePodIP` Annotation 回退\n277:    - [ ] `resolvePodIP` LabelSelector + OwnerReference 回退\n278:    - [ ] `resolvePodIP` 全部失败 → 错误\n279:    - [ ] `rollbackCR` 正常删除\n280:    - [ ] `rollbackCR` AlreadyNotFound → 忽略\n281:    - [ ] `getDynamicClient` auth 关闭 → 返回默认 client\n282:    - [ ] `getDynamicClient` auth 开启 + token cache → 调用 cache\n283:    - [ ] `getDynamicClient` auth 开启 + 无 token → 错误\n284:    - [ ] `buildEntryPoints` 多端口端点构建\n285:    - [ ] `RandString` 长度和字符集验证\n286: \n287: 3. **const.go**\n288:    - [ ] `LastActivityAnnotationKey` == \"last-activity-time\"\n289: \n290: ## Status\n291: \n292: - [ ] Proposal review\n293: - [ ] Implementation\n294: - [ ] Verification\n\n(End of file - total 294 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n\n**Module:** pkg/workloadmanager\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** L\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块补齐缺失的 Go 单元测试，覆盖 reconciler 核心协调逻辑、handler sandbox 创建流程、及顶层常量定义。已有测试（response、lifecycle、delete、metrics）保持不变。目标是提升关键路径代码覆盖率、防止回归、为后续重构提供安全网。\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n1. **reconciler/reconciler_test.go** — `SandboxReconciler` 生命周期测试\n   - `NewSandboxReconciler` 参数校验（nil Store/Clientset/InformerFactory panic）\n   - `Run` 幂等性（重复调用忽略）、cache sync 成功/失败路径\n   - `Enqueue` key 格式（带/不带 namespace）、metrics 触发\n   - `WatchSandboxOnce` 正常返回、超时返回\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775894967781,"end":1775894967788}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775894968991,"sessionID":"ses_2846be6dbffem0trR4hEIofkpE","part":{"id":"prt_d7b96b671001iqiH9ObtGOb8Ae","messageID":"msg_d7b96a8d9001EOoI775NaAPsLv","sessionID":"ses_2846be6dbffem0trR4hEIofkpE","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_1c84702a3bac43ec857ce1b6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/Makefile"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/Makefile</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube — Makefile 构建目标体系\n2: # AR-033: Unified build, test, docker, lint, helm, and python targets\n3: \n4: # ==============================================================================\n5: # Variables and Configuration\n6: # ==============================================================================\n7: \n8: TAG        ?= latest\n9: REGISTRY   ?= agentcube\n10: GOOS       ?= $(shell go env GOOS)\n11: GOARCH     ?= $(shell go env GOARCH)\n12: BIN_DIR    ?= bin\n13: LDFLAGS    ?= -s -w\n14: VERBOSE    ?=\n15: \n16: # Go binaries\n17: GO_BINARIES := router workloadmanager agentd picod\n18: \n19: # Docker images (name -> Dockerfile mapping)\n20: DOCKER_AGENTCUBE_DOCKERFILE := docker/Dockerfile\n21: DOCKER_ROUTER_DOCKERFILE    := docker/Dockerfile.router\n22: DOCKER_PICOD_DOCKERFILE     := docker/Dockerfile.picod\n23: DOCKER_IMAGES               := agentcube router picod\n24: \n25: # Helm chart path\n26: HELM_CHART_DIR := manifests/charts/base\n27: \n28: # Python paths\n29: PYTHON_SDK_DIR  := python-sdk\n30: PYTHON_CLI_DIR  := cmd/cli\n31: \n32: # ==============================================================================\n33: # Verbosity helper\n34: # ==============================================================================\n35: \n36: ifeq ($(VERBOSE),1)\n37:   V =\n38:   Q =\n39: else\n40:   V = @\n41:   Q = @\n42: endif\n43: \n44: # ==============================================================================\n45: # .PHONY declarations\n46: # ==============================================================================\n47: \n48: .PHONY: all build clean test test-coverage test-chart lint fmt vet \\\n49:         docker helm-lint helm-template python-lint python-test ci \\\n50:         build/router build/workloadmanager build/agentd build/picod \\\n51:         docker/agentcube docker/router docker/picod \\\n52:         gen-client\n53: \n54: # ==============================================================================\n55: # Composite Targets\n56: # ==============================================================================\n57: \n58: all: build test lint\n59: \n60: ci: build test test-coverage lint helm-lint\n61: \n62: # ==============================================================================\n63: # Go Build Targets\n64: # ==============================================================================\n65: \n66: build: build/router build/workloadmanager build/agentd build/picod\n67: \n68: build/router:\n69: \t$(Q)mkdir -p $(BIN_DIR)\n70: \t$(Q)echo \"  BUILD   router ($(GOOS)/$(GOARCH))\"\n71: \t$(V)GOOS=$(GOOS) GOARCH=$(GOARCH) go build -ldflags '$(LDFLAGS)' -o $(BIN_DIR)/router ./cmd/router\n72: \n73: build/workloadmanager:\n74: \t$(Q)mkdir -p $(BIN_DIR)\n75: \t$(Q)echo \"  BUILD   workloadmanager ($(GOOS)/$(GOARCH))\"\n76: \t$(V)GOOS=$(GOOS) GOARCH=$(GOARCH) go build -ldflags '$(LDFLAGS)' -o $(BIN_DIR)/workloadmanager ./cmd/workloadmanager\n77: \n78: build/agentd:\n79: \t$(Q)mkdir -p $(BIN_DIR)\n80: \t$(Q)echo \"  BUILD   agentd ($(GOOS)/$(GOARCH))\"\n81: \t$(V)GOOS=$(GOOS) GOARCH=$(GOARCH) go build -ldflags '$(LDFLAGS)' -o $(BIN_DIR)/agentd ./cmd/agentd\n82: \n83: build/picod:\n84: \t$(Q)mkdir -p $(BIN_DIR)\n85: \t$(Q)echo \"  BUILD   picod ($(GOOS)/$(GOARCH))\"\n86: \t$(V)GOOS=$(GOOS) GOARCH=$(GOARCH) go build -ldflags '$(LDFLAGS)' -o $(BIN_DIR)/picod ./cmd/picod\n87: \n88: clean:\n89: \t$(Q)rm -rf $(BIN_DIR)\n90: \t$(Q)echo \"  CLEAN   build artifacts removed\"\n91: \n92: # ==============================================================================\n93: # Docker Build Targets\n94: # ==============================================================================\n95: \n96: docker: $(addprefix docker/,$(DOCKER_IMAGES))\n97: \n98: docker/agentcube:\n99: \t$(Q)echo \"  DOCKER  $(REGISTRY)/agentcube:$(TAG)\"\n100: \t$(V)docker build -t $(REGISTRY)/agentcube:$(TAG) -f $(DOCKER_AGENTCUBE_DOCKERFILE) .\n101: \n102: docker/router:\n103: \t$(Q)echo \"  DOCKER  $(REGISTRY)/router:$(TAG)\"\n104: \t$(V)docker build -t $(REGISTRY)/router:$(TAG) -f $(DOCKER_ROUTER_DOCKERFILE) .\n105: \n106: docker/picod:\n107: \t$(Q)echo \"  DOCKER  $(REGISTRY)/picod:$(TAG)\"\n108: \t$(V)docker build -t $(REGISTRY)/picod:$(TAG) -f $(DOCKER_PICOD_DOCKERFILE) .\n109: \n110: # ==============================================================================\n111: # Test Targets\n112: # ==============================================================================\n113: \n114: test:\n115: \t$(Q)echo \"  TEST    go test ./...\"\n116: \t$(V)go test ./...\n117: \n118: test-coverage:\n119: \t$(Q)echo \"  COVER   go test -coverprofile=coverage.out ./...\"\n120: \t$(V)go test -coverprofile=coverage.out ./...\n121: \n122: test-chart:\n123: \t$(Q)echo \"  TEST    helm chart render\"\n124: \t$(V)bash test/chart/test_render.sh\n125: \n126: # ==============================================================================\n127: # Code Quality Targets\n128: # ==============================================================================\n129: \n130: lint:\n131: \t$(Q)if ! command -v golangci-lint >/dev/null 2>&1; then \\\n132: \t\techo \"ERROR: golangci-lint is required but not installed.\"; \\\n133: \t\texit 1; \\\n134: \tfi\n135: \t$(Q)echo \"  LINT    golangci-lint run\"\n136: \t$(V)golangci-lint run\n137: \n138: fmt:\n139: \t$(Q)echo \"  FMT     go fmt ./...\"\n140: \t$(V)go fmt ./...\n141: \n142: vet:\n143: \t$(Q)echo \"  VET     go vet ./...\"\n144: \t$(V)go vet ./...\n145: \n146: # ==============================================================================\n147: # Helm Targets\n148: # ==============================================================================\n149: \n150: helm-lint:\n151: \t$(Q)if ! command -v helm >/dev/null 2>&1; then \\\n152: \t\techo \"ERROR: helm is required but not installed.\"; \\\n153: \t\texit 1; \\\n154: \tfi\n155: \t$(Q)echo \"  HELM    lint $(HELM_CHART_DIR)\"\n156: \t$(V)helm lint $(HELM_CHART_DIR)\n157: \n158: helm-template:\n159: \t$(Q)if ! command -v helm >/dev/null 2>&1; then \\\n160: \t\techo \"ERROR: helm is required but not installed.\"; \\\n161: \t\texit 1; \\\n162: \tfi\n163: \t$(Q)echo \"  HELM    template $(HELM_CHART_DIR)\"\n164: \t$(V)helm template release $(HELM_CHART_DIR)\n165: \n166: # ==============================================================================\n167: # Python Targets\n168: # ==============================================================================\n169: \n170: python-lint:\n171: \t$(Q)if command -v ruff >/dev/null 2>&1; then \\\n172: \t\techo \"  PYLINT  ruff check $(PYTHON_SDK_DIR) $(PYTHON_CLI_DIR)\"; \\\n173: \t\truff check $(PYTHON_SDK_DIR) $(PYTHON_CLI_DIR); \\\n174: \telif command -v flake8 >/dev/null 2>&1; then \\\n175: \t\techo \"  PYLINT  flake8 $(PYTHON_SDK_DIR) $(PYTHON_CLI_DIR)\"; \\\n176: \t\tflake8 $(PYTHON_SDK_DIR) $(PYTHON_CLI_DIR); \\\n177: \telse \\\n178: \t\techo \"WARNING: No Python lint tool found (ruff or flake8). Install one to enable linting.\"; \\\n179: \tfi\n180: \n181: python-test:\n182: \t$(Q)if command -v pytest >/dev/null 2>&1; then \\\n183: \t\techo \"  PYTEST  pytest $(PYTHON_SDK_DIR)/tests $(PYTHON_CLI_DIR)/tests\"; \\\n184: \t\tpytest $(PYTHON_SDK_DIR)/tests $(PYTHON_CLI_DIR)/tests; \\\n185: \telse \\\n186: \t\techo \"WARNING: pytest is not installed. Install it to run Python tests.\"; \\\n187: \tfi\n188: \n189: # ==============================================================================\n190: # Code Generation\n191: # ==============================================================================\n192: \n193: gen-client:\n194: \t$(Q)echo \"  GEN     client-go (k8s.io/code-generator)\"\n195: \t$(V)bash hack/update-codegen.sh\n\n(End of file - total 195 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube — Makefile 构建目标体系\n# AR-033: Unified build, test, docker, lint, helm, and python targets\n\n# ==============================================================================\n# Variables and Configuration\n# ==============================================================================\n\nTAG        ?= latest\nREGISTRY   ?= agentcube\nGOOS       ?= $(shell go env GOOS)\nGOARCH     ?= $(shell go env GOARCH)\nBIN_DIR    ?= bin\nLDFLAGS    ?= -s -w\nVERBOSE    ?=\n\n# Go binaries\nGO_BINARIES := router workloadmanager agentd picod\n\n# Docker images (name -> Dockerfile mapping)\nDOCKER_AGENTCUBE_DOCKERFILE := docker/Dockerfile","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/Makefile","time":{"start":1775894968984,"end":1775894968989}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775894969196,"sessionID":"ses_2846be6dbffem0trR4hEIofkpE","part":{"id":"prt_d7b96bb5c001XXoh3svynSBghn","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d7b96a8d9001EOoI775NaAPsLv","sessionID":"ses_2846be6dbffem0trR4hEIofkpE","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":25525,"input":25338,"output":146,"reasoning":41,"cache":{"write":0,"read":0}},"cost":0.007302025}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775894972399,"sessionID":"ses_2846be6dbffem0trR4hEIofkpE","part":{"id":"prt_d7b96c7eb001OKL6pR68svofV6","messageID":"msg_d7b96bb8c001t5DrvosBye6TN6","sessionID":"ses_2846be6dbffem0trR4hEIofkpE","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775895137198,"sessionID":"ses_2846be6dbffem0trR4hEIofkpE","part":{"id":"prt_d7b96cc68001t1W22U4sgLXB5S","messageID":"msg_d7b96bb8c001t5DrvosBye6TN6","sessionID":"ses_2846be6dbffem0trR4hEIofkpE","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_55e14060a3a64c4daceb5409","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore cmd and pkg structure","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project at /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z to understand:\n\n1. Read the cmd/ directory structure and main.go files for each binary (router, workloadmanager, agentd, picod, cli)\n2. Read the pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ directory to understand the CRD types\n3. Look at the manifests/charts/base/ to understand the Helm chart structure\n4. Look at the test/ directory structure\n5. Read the project.md file for project context\n\nReturn:\n- Summary of each cmd/ binary's purpose and key endpoints/functionality\n- CRD type definitions (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter specs)\n- Helm chart components\n- Current test/ directory contents\n- Key project context from project.md","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_284691db8ffe96Dt6yRKab7Ahm (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nNow I have a comprehensive view of the project. Here is the full summary:\n\n---\n\n## AgentCube Project Summary\n\n### 1. CMD/ Binaries\n\n#### **router** (`cmd/router/main.go`, `cmd/router/config.go`)\n- **Purpose**: Session-aware HTTP reverse proxy that routes incoming requests to sandbox pods. Acts as the primary ingress for all agent invocations.\n- **Key functionality**:\n  - Listens on port `8080` (configurable via `--port` or `ROUTER_PORT`)\n  - Connects to Kubernetes API via informer-based watch on AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CRDs\n  - Uses Redis/Valkey as a session store for session routing state\n  - JWT-based authentication (RS256) with configurable expiration, issuer, and leeway\n  - Concurrency limiting (default 1000 concurrent requests)\n  - Session lifecycle: check interval (5m), idle timeout (30m), max duration (24h)\n  - Supports TLS and HTTP/2 (h2c)\n- **Key endpoints** (from `pkg/router/server.go`):\n  - `GET /health/live` -- Liveness probe\n  - `GET /health/ready` -- Readiness probe\n  - `GET/POST /v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` -- AgentRuntime invocation proxy\n  - `GET/POST /v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` -- CodeInterpreter invocation proxy\n  - All `/v1/*` routes are protected by JWT auth middleware and concurrency limiting\n\n#### **workloadmanager** (`cmd/workloadmanager/main.go`, `cmd/workloadmanager/config.go`)\n- **Purpose**: Sandbox lifecycle management service. Handles sandbox creation, deletion, status queries, TTL extension, and garbage collection.\n- **Key functionality**:\n  - Listens on port `8080` (configurable via `--port` or `WM_PORT`)\n  - Uses Kubernetes dynamic client, standard clientset, and AgentCube custom clientset\n  - Shared informer factory for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRD watching\n  - Sandbox reconciler with configurable worker count (default 2)\n  - Lifecycle manager with periodic GC for expired/idle sandboxes\n  - Optional Bearer token auth (`--enable-auth`)\n  - Metrics port on `9090`\n- **Key endpoints** (from `cmd/workloadmanager/main.go`):\n  - `GET /health/live` -- Liveness probe\n  - `GET /health/ready` -- Readiness probe\n  - `POST /api/v1/sandboxes` -- Create sandbox (dispatches to AgentRuntime or CodeInterpreter handler based on `kind`)\n  - `DELETE /api/v1/sandboxes/:sessionID` -- Delete sandbox\n  - `GET /api/v1/sandboxes/:sessionID` -- Get sandbox status\n  - `GET /api/v1/sandboxes` -- List all sandboxes\n  - `POST /api/v1/sandboxes/:sessionID/extend` -- Extend sandbox TTL\n\n#### **agentd** (`cmd/agentd/main.go`)\n- **Purpose**: Idle cleanup controller for Sandbox resources. A Kubernetes controller built with `controller-runtime` that watches Sandbox CRs and deletes them when they exceed their session expiration timeout.\n- **Key functionality**:\n  - Uses `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` manager framework\n  - Watches `sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox` resources\n  - Reads the `last-activity-time` annotation on Sandboxes\n  - Deletes sandboxes idle longer than `SessionExpirationTimeout`\n  - No HTTP server; purely a background reconciler\n  - Metrics and health probes disabled (bind address `\"0\"`)\n\n#### **picod** (`cmd/picod/main.go`)\n- **Purpose**: Lightweight daemon that runs **inside** sandbox pods to provide code execution and file management capabilities. Think of it as a minimal in-sandbox API server.\n- **Key functionality**:\n  - Listens on port `8080` (configurable via `--port`)\n  - Workspace directory for file operations (configurable via `--workspace`)\n  - JWT RS256 public-key authentication middleware on all API routes\n  - Command execution with configurable timeout, working directory, environment variables, and path sanitization (prevents directory traversal)\n- **Key endpoints** (from `pkg/picod/server.go`):\n  - `GET /health` -- Health check (returns status, service name, version, uptime)\n  - `POST /api/execute` -- Execute a command (with timeout, working dir, env vars)\n  - `POST /api/files` -- Upload a file\n  - `GET /api/files` -- List files\n  - `GET /api/files/*path` -- Download a specific file\n\n#### **cli** (`cmd/cli/`)\n- **Purpose**: Python-based developer CLI tool for AI agent lifecycle management. Built with Typer + Rich.\n- **Version**: `0.1.0`\n- **Commands** (from `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py`):\n  - `agentcube pack` -- Package an agent workspace (Dockerfile generation, metadata creation)\n  - `agentcube build` -- Build a container image from a packaged agent workspace\n  - `agentcube publish` -- Publish a packaged agent to Kubernetes (supports `agentcube` provider for AgentRuntime CR, or `k8s` provider for plain Deployment/Service)\n  - `agentcube invoke` -- Invoke a deployed agent with a JSON payload\n  - `agentcube status` -- Check the status of a deployed agent\n- **Runtime modules**: `PackRuntime`, `BuildRuntime`, `PublishRuntime`, `InvokeRuntime`, `StatusRuntime`\n\n---\n\n### 2. CRD Type Definitions (`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`)\n\n**API Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n\n#### **AgentRuntime** (`agent_type.go`)\n- **Scope**: Namespaced, plural: `agentruntimes`\n- **Spec**:\n  - `targetPort` ([]TargetPort) -- Ports to expose with path prefix, name, port number, and protocol (HTTP/HTTPS)\n  - `podTemplate` (*SandboxTemplate, **required**) -- Pod template containing labels, annotations, and a full `corev1.PodSpec`\n  - `sessionTimeout` (*metav1.Duration, **required**) -- Session idle timeout\n  - `maxSessionDuration` (*metav1.Duration, **required**) -- Maximum session lifetime\n- **Status**:\n  - `conditions` ([]metav1.Condition) -- Standard Kubernetes conditions\n- **SandboxTemplate**: Wraps labels, annotations, and a full `corev1.PodSpec` for arbitrary pod configuration\n\n#### **CodeInterpreter** (`codeinterpreter_types.go`)\n- **Scope**: Namespaced, plural: `codeinterpreters`\n- **Spec**:\n  - `ports` ([]TargetPort) -- Ports to expose\n  - `template` (*CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate, **required**) -- Simplified sandbox template with: labels, annotations, runtimeClassName, image, imagePullPolicy, imagePullSecrets, environment variables, command, args, and resource requirements\n  - `sessionTimeout` (*metav1.Duration) -- Session idle timeout\n  - `maxSessionDuration` (*metav1.Duration) -- Maximum session lifetime\n  - `warmPoolSize` (*int32) -- Pre-warmed sandbox pool size\n  - `authMode` (AuthModeType, default: `\"picod\"`) -- Authentication mode: `\"picod\"` or `\"none\"`\n- **Status**:\n  - `conditions` ([]metav1.Condition)\n  - `ready` (bool) -- Ready flag\n\n#### **Shared Types** (`shared_types.go`)\n- `ProtocolType`: `\"HTTP\"` or `\"HTTPS\"`\n- `AuthModeType`: `\"picod\"` or `\"none\"`\n- `TargetPort`: `pathPrefix`, `name`, `port` (uint32), `protocol`\n\n#### **Constants** (`constants.go`)\n- `AnnotationKeyRuntime`: `\"agentcube.io/runtime\"`\n- `AnnotationKeyVersion`: `\"agentcube.io/version\"`\n\n---\n\n### 3. Helm Chart Components (`manifests/charts/base/`)\n\n**Chart**: `agentcube` v0.1.0, appVersion 1.0.0\n\n#### **values.yaml** -- Configurable sections:\n- `imagePullSecrets` -- Private registry credentials\n- `redis.addr` / `redis.password` -- Redis/Valkey connection (must be provided at install time)\n- `router` -- Deployment config (replicas, image, service, resources, extraEnv, optional RBAC)\n- `workloadmanager` -- Deployment config (replicas, image, service, resources, extraEnv, RBAC enabled by default)\n- `volcano.scheduler` -- Optional Volcano scheduler integration (disabled by default)\n\n#### **Templates**:\n- `agentcube-router.yaml` -- Deployment + Service for the router component\n  - Liveness: `/health/live` (1s initial delay, 2s period)\n  - Readiness: `/health/ready` (1s initial delay, 2s period)\n  - Env: `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE`, `REDIS_ADDR`, `REDIS_PASSWORD`, `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` (auto-constructed)\n- `workloadmanager.yaml` -- Deployment + Service for the workload manager\n  - Liveness/Readiness: `/health` (10s/5s initial delay, 10s/5s period)\n  - Env: `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE`, `REDIS_ADDR`, `REDIS_PASSWORD`\n- `rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` -- ServiceAccount + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding (always created)\n  - Permissions: `agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxes`, `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxclaims|sandboxtemplates|sandboxwarmpools`, `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters|agentruntimes`, pods, secrets, tokenreviews\n- `rbac/router.yaml` -- ServiceAccount + Role + RoleBinding (conditional, off by default)\n  - Permissions: secrets (namespace-scoped)\n- `rbac/volcano-scheduler.yaml` -- Full Volcano scheduler RBAC (conditional)\n- `_helpers.tpl` -- Standard Helm helpers (name, fullname, labels, selectorLabels, rbacName, rbacBindingName)\n\n#### **CRDs** (`crds/`):\n- `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml`\n- `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml`\n\n---\n\n### 4. Test/ Directory Contents\n\n```\ntest/\n  chart/\n    test_render.sh      -- 271-line bash test suite for Helm chart validation (AR-030)\n  makefile/\n    test_makefile.sh    -- 375-line bash test suite for Makefile targets (AR-033)\n```\n\n**`test/chart/test_render.sh`** validates:\n- Chart.yaml metadata (apiVersion, name, version, appVersion)\n- values.yaml structure and defaults\n- Helm lint and default rendering (2 Deployments, 2 Services, 1 ClusterRole, 1 ServiceAccount)\n- Workload Manager template correctness (name, namespace, image, probes, env vars, service account)\n- Router template correctness (name, image, WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL, probes, args, service selector)\n- WM RBAC (ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding with correct API groups)\n- Router RBAC conditional behavior (off by default, creates Role+RoleBinding when enabled)\n- Volcano scheduler conditional behavior\n- Scenario overrides (custom replicas, images, extraEnv, imagePullSecrets, namespace scoping)\n- CRD verification (both CRDs present, correct group/scope/version, required fields)\n- Name override functionality\n\n**`test/makefile/test_makefile.sh`** validates:\n- Makefile existence and parseability\n- `.PHONY` declarations (all, build, clean, test, test-coverage, test-chart, lint, fmt, vet, docker, helm-lint, helm-template, python-lint, python-test, ci, build/*, docker/*)\n- Default variable values (TAG=latest, REGISTRY=agentcube, BIN_DIR=bin, LDFLAGS=-s -w)\n- Variable override support (TAG, REGISTRY, GOOS, GOARCH)\n- Build targets (all binaries, individual binaries, isolation between build/<binary> targets)\n- Clean target (removes bin/, idempotent)\n- Docker targets (dry-run verification for docker, docker/router, docker/picod)\n- Test/coverage/chart test dry-runs\n- Lint/fmt/vet targets\n- Helm-lint/helm-template targets\n- Python-lint/python-test targets\n- `all` and `ci` composite targets\n- .PHONY overriding same-name files\n- VERBOSE mode\n- LDFLAGS customization\n- BIN_DIR customization\n\n---\n\n### 5. Key Project Context (from `project.md`)\n\n- **Full name**: AgentCube -- A Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents\n- **Source**: `github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube` (Go module: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`)\n- **Core purpose**: Provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup)\n- **Tech stack**:\n  - Go 1.24 (server), Python 3.10+ (CLI/SDK)\n  - Gin (Go HTTP), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example)\n  - CRDs: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`, controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox`\n  - Storage: Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go)\n  - Auth: JWT RS256, K8s TokenReview\n  - Packaging: Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD\n  - Docs: Docusaurus 3.x\n- **Architecture flow**:\n  ```\n  Client / SDK / CLI\n    -> Router (Deployment :8080)\n       <-> Redis/Valkey (session store)\n       -> WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\n          <-> Redis/Valkey\n          -> K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\n  Sandbox Pods (with optional PicoD daemon)\n  Agentd (idle cleanup controller)\n  Optional: Volcano vc-agent-scheduler\n  ```\n- **Conventions**: Go packages under `pkg/`, binaries under `cmd/`, Python CLI at `cmd/cli/`, K8s resources use `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` API group\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_284691db8ffe96Dt6yRKab7Ahm","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore cmd and pkg structure","time":{"start":1775894979138,"end":1775895137195}}}}
